inline_comments.message:
I know that this is not raised in the Sonar issue but as I see it here, this error message will do nothing except annoy a user.

Could you improve this exception message to something like:
LOGGER.error ("Save of configuration to file {} failed", CONFIG_HOME + File.separator + configurationName + ".json", e);

Better still declare a string variable for the file name before the "try"
String fileName = CONFIG_HOME + File.separator + configurationName + ".json";

and then use the variable fileName wherever is appropriate.
